Fantasy2C
Version: 1.2.52

TODO/BUGS:
-MIDI Device has Memory Leak
-Software Rendering

Version History:

2 Februar 2011 released version 1.2.52 of Fantasy2C
Change log:
	-Fixed: Operator != Color,ColorTone, returns false value
	-Added: Function Timer::pause(),start(), pause,stop and start functions  
	-Fixed: Function AudioFile::loadDevice(...), Memory Leak in static Member
	-Added: BlendType, light and mask for LightMap and Masking Effect
	-Update: Function Bitmap/AudioFile,Font::loadFile(...) throw a LogError with an ErrorCode
	-New: LogError Class, Error Code Makros like NO_ERROR, NO_SUCH_FILE_OR_DIR,....
	-Fixed: Function FontSprite::getStringSize(...), add factor zoom_x and zoom_y
	-Updated: GLFW DLL
	-New: Software Rendering Engine
	-New: Vector2,3,4 Class, Vector with x,y,z,w
	-New: Matrix3,4 Class, 3x3 and 4x4  Matrix
	-New: Color3,4 Class, Color with RGBA
	-New: Texture2D Class, Managment 2D texturen with mipmap level. 

30 July 2010 released version 1.2.15 of Fantasy2C
Change log:
	-Added: Function Rect::collision(...),get collision of rect
	-New: Timer class, simple Timer
	-Fixed: ColorTone::ColorTonetoRGB(...), convert CMY in RGB
	-Fixed: RenderManager::setScissorInBottomLeftMode(...),convert BottomLeft to TopLeft Mode
	-Updated: Bitmap::fillRect(...) function optimized
	-Added: Function Bitmap::clearRect(...), Clear an area (Set pixels on 0).
	-Fixed: Spacing of the letters adapted (FontSprite)
	-Added: Function Window::getScreen/WindowSize(...), get Window/Screen Size as F2C::Rect
	-Fixed: Remove glGenTexture in (Default) Constructors (Sprite,Plane,...)
	-New: RenderManager class, Some usefull Rendering functions. (for Sprite classes)
	-Added: Function Bitmap::isChanged(), Is Bitmap changed, like setPixel,scale,blt,fillRect
	-Added: Function Sprite::enableGLDrawArray(), Enable/Disable use glDrawArray in (Simple)Sprite,Plane,FontSprite and AraySprite
	-Added: Function FontSprite::getStringSize(...), get size(in pixel) of a string
	-Added: Function TTFFTont::loadBitmap(...), load Font from BitmapFont
	-Added: Function Bitmap::blt(...), normal blt-function for pixel arrays (not Bitmap class)
	-Updated: Bitmap::blt(...) function optimized
	-New: stream-Operator(<<,>>) to write/read F2C classes(Sprite,Bitmap,Color,Rect,...) into/from stream


